data.description: Welcome to 57229 Jarana Ct! A beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home nicely situated on a corner lot in the highly desirable Copper Hills neighborhood of Yucca Valley. This picture-perfect home features 1,560 sqft of living space with vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, central heat/AC and leased solar to keep costs low year round (only $145 a month, buyer to assume lease). The spacious living room adorns earth-toned tile, a lovely fireplace and large windows that let in an abundance of natural light. Just off the living room is the formal dining space & kitchen which is complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space and a walk-in pantry. This home's modern/boho-inspired style & functional floor-plan is one to be desired. The primary bedroom boasts high ceilings, french doors that lead to the backyard and an ensuite bathroom with a dual sink vanity, second closet space and a walk-in shower. There is also a convenient indoor laundry room that leads to the attached/finished 3 car garage. Outside you'll be delighted to find a lovely covered patio, fully fenced yard with RV access and parking, a grassy play area and plenty of space to entertain or relax around a firepit on a starry desert night. Come take a look & let this home's light, bright & charming allure do the rest. Your new desert home or weekend retreat awaits! **SELLER'S ARE WILLING TO GIVE CONCESSIONS TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS AND OR RATE BUY-DOWN!!**
